A junior developer has downloaded a sample Amazon S3 bucket policy to make changes to it based on new
          company-wide access policies. He has requested your help in understanding this bucket policy.
As a Solutions Architect, which of the following would you identify as the correct description for the given
          policy?
{
            "Version": "2012-10-17",
            "Id": "S3PolicyId1",
            "Statement": [
            {
            "Sid": "IPAllow",
            "Effect": "Allow",
            "Principal": "*",
            "Action": "s3:*",
            "Resource": "arn:aws:s3:::examplebucket/*",
            "Condition": {
            "IpAddress": {"aws:SourceIp": "54.240.143.0/24"},
            "NotIpAddress": {"aws:SourceIp": "54.240.143.188/32"}
            }
            }
            ]
            }
